lity and a semantic component.  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aBlocks (Toys) 0aEducationxPhilosophy. 4aBuilding Blocks. 4aCultural History. 4aCultural Studies. 4aCultural Techniques. 4aDesign. 4aEducation. 4aHistory of Education. 4aHistory of Technology. 4aKindergarten. 4aModularization. 4aTechnology. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aCultural Studies.  aDesign.  aHistory of Education.  aHistory of Technology.  aTechnology.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2020 Englishz978311070472308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP ROW Ebook Package English 2020z978311069630108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311068961740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839447819zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839447819423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839447819/original  a978-3-11-068961-7  transcript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  a978-3-11-069630-1  PP ROW Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLE